arctis-sound-manager (1.0.12-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Fix: LADSPA mic processing (noise gate, RNNoise, compressor) silently broken — missing = in PipeWire control syntax
  * Fix: check_and_fix_stale_configs output channel routing
  * Fix: get_physical_source() now retries 15x on PulseAudio error
  * Fix: D-Bus async methods guard against connection failure, polling loop survives transient errors

